    "body" : "<p>This simplest (using Calendar, sorry) is:</p>\n\n<pre><code> int year = Calendar.getInstance().get(Calendar.YEAR);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>There is also the new <a href=\"https://jsr-310.dev.java.net/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Date and Time API JSR</a>, as well as <a href=\"http://joda-time.sourceforge.net/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Joda Time</a></p>\n"
