    "body" : "<p>Using Java 8's time API (assuming you are happy to get the year in your system's default time zone), you could use <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/time/Year.html#now--\" rel=\"noreferrer\">the <code>Year::now</code> method</a>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>int year = Year.now().getValue();\n</code></pre>\n"
